29/11/2009
ATHENS, Greece -- Police arrested an Albanian citizen Friday (November 27th) who allegedly packed 159kg of raw cannabis onto the luggage rack of his car.
He was detained in the northern region of Tesprotija, after the car was found to have been stolen from the town of Patra a month ago.
While inspecting the vehicle, police found the drugs.
(MIA - 27/11/09)
